      <title>美国财政部将于周二推出措施避免突破债务上限</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-will-hit-debt-limit-tuesday-yellen-says-letter-2025-01-17/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国财政部长珍妮特耶伦表示，政府将于周二达到法定借款限额，并开始采取“非常措施”以避免突破上限并冒着潜在的灾难性违约风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-will-hit-debt-limit-tuesday-yellen-says-letter-2025-01-17/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 21:43:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
